      "text": "水着のグラビア撮影だ……天動さんは確か\nそういう仕事をしたことはなかっただろう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Posing for photos in a swimsuit…\nTendo-san haven’t done that before‚ have you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 238.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-rui022.m4a",
      "text": "な、ないです、私、バンプロにいた頃は\nそういう仕事をやったことがなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-no‚ I never did this type of work\nwhile I was with Van Productions…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 245.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-rui023.m4a",
      "text": "決して、そういった仕事を悪く思ってる訳では\nないんですけど……でも、恥ずかしいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not that I have anything against it.\nIt’s just… well‚ a little shy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 251.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_02_01-koh019.m4a",
      "text": "分かってる。俺も無理強いはしたくない\n一応、話はしておこうって思っただけで――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand. You don’t have to do it if you don’t want to.\nI just wanted to let you know about it—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 260.03333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
